              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Trustpilot score is 1.9/5 — billing complaints are common</li>
                <li>GTM pivot has confused original users</li>
                <li>No SEO features, no CMS integration</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Marketing teams that want AI-powered GTM workflows over pure writing quality.</div>
            <a href="/alternatives/copy-ai/" class="tool-cta-btn">Read alternatives →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">05</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Frase</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best for SEO content + briefs</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$49<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Starter plan</div>
